SUMMARY:Piece by Piece\, A Queer Craft Night
DESCRIPTION:Just like mosaics\, our stories are made up of many pieces. J
 oin La Casa's Queer initiative as we create DIY mosaic picture frames and
  celebrate the beauty in every fragment of who we are.Materials and snack
 s provided. Bring a photo or make the frame for a future memory.&#160\;La
  Casa Queer Initiative creates an inclusive and affirming space for LGBTQ
 + students to connect\, find support\, and build community.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">
 Just like mosaics\, our stories are made up of many pieces. Join La Casa'
 s Queer initiative as we create DIY mosaic picture frames and celebrate t
 he beauty in every fragment of who we are.<br /></span></p><p><span data-
 olk-copy-source="MessageBody">Materials and snacks provided. Bring a phot
 o or make the frame for a future memory.&#160\;</span></p><p><span data-o
 lk-copy-source="MessageBody">La Casa Queer Initiative creates an inclusiv
 e and affirming space for LGBTQ+ students to connect\, find support\, and
  build community.</span></p>
