SUMMARY:Breaking Barriers: Latina Leaders in STEM
DESCRIPTION:What does it mean to lead and innovate as a Latina in STEM? J
 oin us for an empowering discussion with trailblazing professionals who a
 re making a lasting impact in their industry. Through personal stories an
 d professional insights\, they will highlight the importance of persevera
 nce\, representation\, and community support in achieving success. Light 
 dinner served.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">
 What does it mean to lead and innovate as a Latina in STEM? Join us for a
 n empowering discussion with trailblazing professionals who are making a 
 lasting impact in their industry. Through personal stories and profession
 al insights\, they will highlight the importance of perseverance\, repres
 entation\, and community support in achieving success. Light dinner serve
 d.</span></p>
