DESCRIPTION:Held biannually\, the ChĂˇvez Symposium allows students to co
 nduct research focusing on Latinxs in the U.S. and in transnational conte
 xts. Undergraduate students undertake a sustained research project of the
 ir choosing\, culminating in a two-day symposium to showcase their resear
 ch. The ChĂˇvez Symposium bridges undergraduate\, graduate\, and faculty 
 research by partnering each undergraduate participant with a mentor who h
 elps plan and directs the research.
