SUMMARY:Asquerosamente Rico: Cooking on a Budget\, Part 3
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we learn to cook a delicious dish called Pollo Sal
 tado. Pollo Saltado\, a traditional Peruvian chicken stir-fry dish\, is a
  fusion meal influenced by Chinese immigration\, making it a 'Chifa.' Per
 uvian cuisine has been greatly influenced and inspired by Chinese immigra
 nts who came to Peru in the 1800s.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><span data-olk-copy-source="MessageBody">
 Join us as we learn to cook a delicious dish called Pollo Saltado. Pollo 
 Saltado\, a traditional Peruvian chicken stir-fry dish\, is a fusion meal
  influenced by Chinese immigration\, making it a 'Chifa.' Peruvian cuisin
 e has been greatly influenced and inspired by Chinese immigrants who came
  to Peru in the 1800s.</span></p>
